                "title": "Yuuban Meigen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Windfavored</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Windfavored</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached performs a Normal Attack:</span> DMG dealt +2. If the opponent has characters on standby, then this Skill will deal damage to the next opposing character on standby instead.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/052cd901b44cef8359f0bebb98404194_2746972486982835191.png",
