                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hanega: Song of the Wind"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 7 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span>. If the character has <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Windfavored</span> attached, then remove it and increase DMG by 1.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Windfavored</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached performs a Normal Attack:</span> DMG dealt +2. If the opponent has characters on standby, then this Skill will deal damage to the next opposing character on standby instead.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/5a55e705974f27b8bb86c628019d5ad9_6705839974041238203.png",
